'''Fùi-sên''' (Comet), siu̍k-chhṳ̂n '''Só-pá-sên''' (掃把星), he yù [[pên]] kèu-sṳ̀n ke [[Thai-yòng-hì]] [[Séu-thiên-thí]], tông kì chêu-hiong [[Ngit-tèu]] chiap-khiûn sṳ̀, fi pûn kâ-ngie̍t pin-chhiâ khôi-sṳ́ [[sṳt-hì]], chán-sṳ chhut khó-kien ke [[Thai-hì-chhèn]], ya chhiu-he [[fùi-fat]], yû sṳ̀ ya-fi yû [[fùi-mî]]. Liá-chúng hien-siong he yù [[Ngit-tèu Fuk-sa]] lâu [[Ngit-tèu-fûng]] khiung-thùng tui [[fùi-fu̍t]] chok-yung chho-sṳ̀n ke. Fùi-fu̍t he yù sûng san-ke [[pên]], [[Chhṳ̀n-âi]], lâu [[Séu-ngâm-sa̍k]] kèu-sṳ̀n ke.
